  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\"/_SYSTEM/scripts/build-claude-md.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**Fichier `_SYSTEM/scripts/build-claude-md.sh`** :
```bash
#!/bin/bash
cd "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR"

# Concatène tous les fichiers sources dans l'ordre
